javax.xml.crypto
Interface NodeSetData

All Superinterfaces:
Data
All Known Implementing Classes:
DOMNodeSetData
public interface NodeSetData
extends Data

An abstract representation of a Data type containing a node-set. The type (class) and ordering of the nodes contained in the set are not defined by this class; instead that behavior should be defined by NodeSetData subclasses.

Method Summary
 Iterator iterator()
          Returns a read-only iterator over the nodes contained in this NodeSetData.
 

Method Detail

iterator

public Iterator iterator()
Returns a read-only iterator over the nodes contained in this NodeSetData. Attempts to modify the returned iterator via the remove method throw UnsupportedOperationException.

Returns:
an Iterator over the nodes in this NodeSetData
